---
// Banner CTA exclusivo de la página About — tono personal, fondo azul
---

<section
  class="px-6 py-28 md:py-36 overflow-hidden relative bg-brand-yellow"
  style="background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 10% 80%, rgba(25,25,25,0.10) 0%, transparent 55%), radial-gradient(ellipse at 90% 10%, rgba(250,246,239,0.18) 0%, transparent 55%);"
>
  <!-- Elemento decorativo -->
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-24 -top-16 w-md h-112 rounded-full border border-base-ink/10 opacity-30"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-12 -top-4 w-72 h-72 rounded-full border border-base-ink/8 opacity-20"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p
        class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-base-ink/50 mb-6 animate-fade-in-up timeline-view animate-range-[entry_0%_cover_18%]"
      >
        ¿Conectamos?
      </p>
      <h2
        class="font-display text-[clamp(2.4rem,5vw,4rem)] font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.03em] text-base-ink mb-6 animate-fade-in-up timeline-view animate-range-[entry_0%_cover_20%]"
      >
        Si llegaste hasta aquí,<br />
        <span class="italic">algo te dice</span> que somos<br />
        lo que buscas.
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-base-ink/65 text-[1.05rem] leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-md animate-fade-in-up timeline-view animate-range-[entry_3%_cover_22%]"
      >
        No hace falta que tengas todo claro. Cuéntanos dónde estás y hacia dónde
        quieres ir — lo demás lo vemos juntos.
      </p>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 animate-fade-in-up timeline-view animate-range-[entry_5%_cover_25%]"
      >
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-block bg-base-ink text-base-bg font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-base-ink/80 transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          Cuéntanos tu proyecto
        </a>
        <a
          href="/servicios"
          class="inline-block border-[1.5px] border-base-ink/30 text-base-ink font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-base-ink/[0.07] transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          Ver qué hacemos →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
